view: "First quarter 2013 results announcement"
},
publicationdate: "2013-05-02T07:00:00Z",
title: "First quarter 2013 results announcement",
summary: "On Thursday, May 2, 2013 at 07.00 BST (08.00 CEST and 02.00 EDT) Royal Dutch Shell plc will release its first quarter results and first quarter interim dividend announcement for 2013. ",
maintext: "<h2>Royal Dutch Shell Chief Executive Officer Peter Voser commented:</h2><p>&nbsp;“Our industry continues to see significant energy price volatility as a result of economic and political developments. Oil prices have fallen recently but Shell is implementing a long-term, competitive and innovative strategy against this volatile backdrop.”</p> <p>“Shell's underlying CCS earnings were $7.5 billion for the quarter, a 2% increase in CCS earnings per share from the first quarter of 2012. These results were underpinned by Shell's growth projects, an improvement in downstream profitability, and were delivered despite a difficult security environment in Nigeria.”</p> <p>“Our profits pay for Shell's dividends and investment in new projects to ensure affordable and reliable energy supplies for our customers, and to add value for our shareholders.”</p> <p>“Shell is investing for profitable growth, whilst maintaining strong capital discipline. We are developing some 30 new projects and maturing a series of further opportunities for investment. So far this year, we’ve seen the growth impact of recent start ups and we took four final investment decisions in petrochemicals, deepwater, and LNG.”</p> <p>“We continue to take a dynamic approach to portfolio” continued Voser. “Asset sales - $0.6 billion in the first quarter and over $21 billion in the last three years - improve our capital efficiency and can bring in strategic partners. We use selective acquisitions to refresh our opportunity set.”</p> <p>Voser commented “We distributed $11 billion of dividends over the last year, the highest in our industry, and today we confirm a 5% rise in our dividend to $0.45 per share.”</p> <p>He concluded “Dividends are Shell’s main route for returning cash to shareholders. Our improving cash flow also enables us to accelerate our share buyback programme, this year so far we have repurchased some $1.2 billion of shares by the end of April. In the current environment we would expect to more than offset the scrip dividend issue this year, and we are determined to implement the policy to offset dilution over the business cycle. This underlines our commitment to shareholder returns.”</p><img src="http://s02.static-shell.com/content/dam/shell/static/investor/imgs/240-wide/peter-voser.jpg" alt="Peter Voser"/><h2>First quarter 2013 results video comment</h2><ul><li><a href="http://www.shell.com/global/aboutshell/investor/financial-information/quarterlyresults/archive/2013/q1-2013/1st-quarter-2013-unaudited-results/video.html">Watch Simon Henry, Chief Financial Officer of Royal Dutch Shell plc, comment on the 2013 first quarter results</a></li></ul><h2>First quarter 2013 results documents</h2><ul><li><a href="http://www.shell.com/global/aboutshell/investor/financial-information/quarterlyresults/archive/2013/q1-2013/1st-quarter-2013-unaudited-results.html">Online version of Quarterly Results Announcement (results in full)</a></li><li><a href="http://s06.static-shell.com/content/dam/shell-new/local/corporate/corporate/downloads/quarterly-results/2013/q1/q1-2013-qra.pdf">PDF of Quarterly Results Announcement (results in full)</a></li></ul><ul><li><a href="http://s02.static-shell.com/content/dam/shell-new/local/corporate/corporate/downloads/quarterly-results/2013/q1/q1-2013-suppl-finandopdisclosure.xls">Excel of Supplementary financial and operational disclosure</a></li><li><a href="http://s04.static-shell.com/content/dam/shell-new/local/corporate/corporate/downloads/quarterly-results/2013/q1/q1-2013-suppl-finandopdisclosure.pdf">PDF of Supplementary financial and operational disclosure</a></li></ul><h2>Restatement of Supplementary financial and operational disclosure</h2><p>This version of the Supplementary financial and operational disclosure shows variances compared with previously-published information for periods Q4 2008-Q4 2012, as a result of the adoption of revised IAS 19 Employee Benefits on January 1, 2013, with retrospective effect.</p><ul><li><a href="http://s01.static-shell.com/content/dam/shell-new/local/corporate/corporate/downloads/quarterly-results/2013/q1/q1-2013-suppl-finandopdisclosure-restatement.pdf">PDF of restatement of Supplementary financial and operational disclosure</a></li><li><a href="http://s03.static-shell.com/content/dam/shell-new/local/corporate/corporate/downloads/quarterly-results/2013/q1/q1-2013-suppl-finandopdisclosure-restatement.xls">Excel of restatement of Supplementary financial and operational disclosure</a></li></ul><h2>First quarter 2013 results webcast</h2><p>Simon Henry, Chief Financial Officer of Royal Dutch Shell hosted audio webcasts of the first quarter results 2013 on Thursday May 2 2013.</p><ul><li><a href="http://cache.merchantcantos.com/webcast/static/ec2mc/4000/5275/5345/10812/Lobby/default.htm">Analyst webcast</a></li><li><a href="http://cache.merchantcantos.com/webcast/static/ec2mc/4000/5275/5345/10816/Lobby/default.htm">Media webcast</a></li></ul><ul><li><a href="http://s00.static-shell.com/content/dam/shell-new/local/corporate/corporate/downloads/quarterly-results/2013/q1/q1-2013-media-presentation-transcript.pdf">PDF of transcript of presentation to media</a></li><li><a href="http://s00.static-shell.com/content/dam/shell-new/local/corporate/corporate/downloads/quarterly-results/2013/q1/q1-2013-analyst-presentation-transcript.pdf">PDF of transcript of presentation to analysts</a></li><li><a href="http://s00.static-shell.com/content/dam/shell-new/local/corporate/corporate/downloads/quarterly-results/2013/q1/q1-2013-presentation-slides-final.pdf">PDF of presentation slides</a></li></ul><p><sup>* If you are accessing this page on an iPad or iPhone,&nbsp;please download&nbsp;and install our </sup><a standard_icon="inactive_icon" href="http://www.shell.com/global/aboutshell/investor/news-and-library/follow-us/app.html"><sup>Investor &amp; Media app</sup></a><sup> and go to the Results section to listen to these webcasts.</sup></p><h2>First quarter 2013 dividend announcement</h2><a href="http://www.shell.com/global/aboutshell/investor/dividend-information/historical-payments/2013/q1.html">First quarter 2013 interim dividend announcement</a>",
