title: "Royal Dutch Shell plc: issuance of new shares",
summary: "Royal Dutch Shell plc announces that it has today issued 25,586,312 A Ordinary shares in relation to the scrip dividend programme for the fourth quarter 2012 interim dividend.",
maintext: "<p>Following this issue and the cancellation of shares previously bought back and announced, the total number of A shares in issuance is 3,797,974,999 and the total number of B shares is 2,599,848,071.&nbsp; Royal Dutch Shell plc holds no ordinary shares in Treasury.</p> <p>This announcement will be available on <a href="http://www.shell.com/investor">http://www.shell.com/investor</a>.</p> <p>March 28, 2013</p> <p>Mark Edwards<br /> Deputy Company Secretary</p><h2>Enquiries</h2><p><b>Media</b><br /> International: +44 207 934 5550<br /> USA: +1 713 241 4544</p> <p><b>Investor Relations</b><br /> International: + 31 70 377 4540<br /> North America: +1 713 241 1042</p>",
