summary: "<p>Shell held a field visit for Socially Responsible Investors in Port Harcourt, Nigeria.</p>",
maintext: "<p>During the visit, shareholders were given presentations by senior Shell and Shell Petroleum Development Company (SPDC) representatives on topics such as the ongoing flare reduction program, the response to the UNEP report and the ongoing situation regarding illegal bunkering.&nbsp; These presentations are available for download below:</p><h2>Shell In Nigeria & SPDC JV Overview</h2><ul><li><a href="http://s03.static-shell.com/content/dam/shell/static/investor/downloads/presentations/2012/overview-sri-shelloperationsnigeria10102012.pdf">Ian Craig (EVP Sub-Saharan Africa) and Mutiu Sunmonu (Managing Director SPDC) - Shell In Nigeria & SPDC JV Overview</a></li></ul><h2>SPDC Flares Reduction Programme</h2><ul><li><a href="http://s05.static-shell.com/content/dam/shell/static/investor/downloads/presentations/2012/flaring-sri-shelloperationsnigeria10102012.pdf">Muhammad Shittu (GM Flared Gas) – SPDC Flares Reduction Programme</a></li></ul><h2>UNEP Report & Response</h2><ul><li><a href="http://s06.static-shell.com/content/dam/shell/static/investor/downloads/presentations/2012/unep-sri-shell-operationsnigeria10102012.pdf">Augustine Igbuku (Ogoni Restoration Project Manager) - UNEP Report & Response</a></li></ul><h2>Sustainable Development & Community Relations</h2><ul><li><a href="http://s07.static-shell.com/content/dam/shell/static/investor/downloads/presentations/2012/community-developmentsrishelloperationsnigeria10102012.pdf">Phillip Mshelbila (Sustainable Development & Community Relations Manager) - Sustainable Development & Community Relations</a></li></ul><h2>Spills and Remediation</h2><ul><li><a href="http://s05.static-shell.com/content/dam/shell/static/investor/downloads/presentations/2012/spills-remediationsrishelloperationsnigeria10102012.pdf">Jurgen Janzen (Pipeline Asset Manager) - Spills and Remediation</a></li></ul><h2>Nigeria Financing Considerations</h2><ul><li><a href="http://s03.static-shell.com/content/dam/shell/static/investor/downloads/prese