summary: "<p>Shell held a field visit for Socially Responsible Investors in Houston and in the Haynesville gas field, Louisiana, at which Russ Ford, EVP onshore gas, John Hollowell, EVP deepwater and Paul Goodfellow, VP production onshore gas all presented.</p>",
maintext: "<p>The focus of the presentations and visit was to illustrate Shell’s tight gas operations in the context of sustainable development and our commitment to responsible deepwater operations.</p><h2>Russ Ford – Tight gas overview</h2><ul><li><a href="http://s07.static-shell.com/content/dam/shell/static/investor/downloads/presentations/2011/sri-tight-gas-deepwaterrussford29112011.pdf">Presentation by Russ Ford – Tight gas overview</a></li></ul><h2>Paul Goodfellow– Haynesville operations and operating principles</h2><ul><li><a href="http://s06.static-shell.com/content/dam/shell/static/investor/downloads/presentations/2011/sri-tight-gas-deepwaterpaulgoodfellow29112011.pdf">Presentation by Paul Goodfellow– Haynesville operations and operating principles</a></li></ul><h2>John Hollowell – Deepwater operations</h2><ul><li><a href="http://s06.static-shell.com/content/dam/shell/static/investor/downloads/presentations/2011/sri-tight-gas-deepwaterjohnhollowell29112011.pdf">Presentation by John Hollowell – Deepwater operations</a></li></ul>",
