title: "Safety in Shell – brochure downloads",
summary: "<p>We have a comprehensive set of business principles and rigorous standards covering health, safety, security, the environment and social performance.&#160; Our approach to safety includes ensuring that our facilities are well designed and maintained, and that our operations are safe and reliable. In the event of a spill, we follow strict emergency response procedures.</p>",
maintext: "<p><strong>HSSE in Shell</strong><br />We manage health, safety, security, the environment and social performance in a systematic way to continually improve our performance.</p><ul><li><a href="http://s08.static-shell.com/content/dam/shell-new/local/corporate/corporate/downloads/pdf/HSSE-in-shell.pdf">HSSE in Shell</a></li></ul><p><strong>Process safety in Shell</strong><br />We work to ensure our facilities are well designed, safely operated, and properly inspected and maintained.</p><ul><li><a href="http://s05.static-shell.com/content/dam/shell/static/environment-society/downloads/safety/process-safety-inshelllr.pdf">Process safety in Shell</a></li></ul><p><strong>Wellbore integrity management</strong><br />We aim to be an industry leader in well design, construction and management.</p><ul><li><a href="http://s02.static-shell.com/content/dam/shell/static/environment-society/downloads/safety/wellbore-brochurelnv5lr2010.pdf">Wellbore integrity management</a></li></ul><p><strong>Oil spill emergency response</strong><br />We plan, prepare and practice our emergency response to incidents to limit consequences for people and the environment.</p><ul><li><a href="http://s01.static-shell.com/content/dam/shell/static/environment-society/downloads/safety/oil-spill-emergencyresponselr.pdf">Oil spill emergency response</a></li></ul><p><strong>Shipping safety and marine risk management</strong> <br />Our rigorous set of controls and assurance measures are designed to ensure safe and reliable shipping operations.</p><ul><li><a href="http://s00.static-shell.com/content/dam/shell/static/environment-society/downloads/safety/shipping-brochurelr.pdf">Shipping safety and marine risk management</a></li></ul><p><strong>Road safety brochure<br /></strong>We help keep our drivers safe through training programmes, by limiting their journeys, and by enforcing our global road safety standards. We work with communities and global partners to improve road safety in the countries where we operate.</p><ul><li><a href="http://s00.static-shell.com/content/dam/shell/static/environment-society/downloads/safety/roadsafety-brochure.pdf">Shell road safety brochure</a></li></ul>",
