title: "2012 Management Day London/New York - Global Gas Perspectives and Asia Pacific Outlook",
summary: "<p>Shell hosted a management day with investors in London (Wednesday 14th November 2012) and New York (Thursday 15th November 2012) focusing on global gas perspectives and Asia Pacific outlook. Presentations were lead by Chief Executive Officer, Peter Voser and Chief Financial Officer, Simon Henry followed by Andrew Brown (Director Upstream International) and Matthias Bichsel (Director Projects & Technology).</p>",
maintext: "<h2>Media release</h2><ul><li><a href="http://www.shell.com/global/aboutshell/media/news-and-media-releases/2012/shell-integrated-gas-strategy-141112.html">Strong global gas demand underpin Shell's integrated gas strategy</a></li></ul><h2>Video message from CEO, Peter Voser on Shell’s integrated gas strategy</h2><iframe src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/eGv0cCF5DZI?rel=0"></iframe><ul><li><a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eGv0cCF5DZI">Watch this video on YouTube</a></li></ul><h2>Slides from management day presentations</h2><ul><li><a href="http://s07.static-shell.com/content/dam/shell/static/investor/downloads/presentations/2012/asia-pac-roundtablepresentationtranscript15112012.pdf">PDF of transcript from management day presentations</a></li><li><a href="http://s04.static-shell.com/content/dam/shell/static/investor/downloads/presentations/2012/asia-pac-roundtablepresentationslides14112012.pdf">PDF of slides from management day presentations</a></li></ul><h2>Audio webcast of New York presentation and Q&A session</h2><p>Audio webcast of the Royal Dutch Shell plc management day focusing on Global gas perspectives and Asia Pacific outlook on November 15, 2012 at 10:30 EST/16:30 CET. There was a plenary presentations followed by a Q&amp;A session.</p><ul><li><a href="http://cache.cantos.com/webcast/static/ec2/4000/5275/10319/10568/Lobby/default.htm">Audio webcast of New York presentation and Q&A session</a></li></ul>",
