title: "Unusual innovation for the future – watch the video",
summary: "<p>Shell Chief Scientists discuss extraordinary and unusual innovative solutions being developed to meet future energy needs. Watch the video. </p> ",
maintext: "<p>By 2050, the world’s population could grow to 9 billion people, up from about 7 billion today. This growing population and rising prosperity around the world will push up global energy demand, and, for the foreseeable future, most people will depend on fossil fuels for the majority of their energy.</p><iframe src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/w1-3hqWxNs4?rel=0"></iframe><ul><li><a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w1-3hqWxNs4">Watch this video on YouTube</a></li></ul>",
