view: "Driving innovation to supply energy for the future"
},
publicationdate: "2011-11-09T11:05:00Z",
title: "Driving innovation to supply energy for the future – video ",
summary: "<p>Shell’s Chief Scientists are thought leaders in their own specialised areas. Meet them to see how they work to overcome challenges and drive innovation forward.</p> ",
maintext: "<p>Shell’s Chief Scientists discuss how industry, governments and society must work together to tackle the challenge of meeting rising energy needs with lower CO<sub>2</sub> emissions. With the faster development of technologies over recent years, they suggest that the industry could be on the brink of a technology revolution.</p><iframe src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/SoIJ3IPjOG8?rel=0"></iframe><ul><li><a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SoIJ3IPjOG8">Watch this video on YouTube</a></li></ul>",
